        <strong style="font-size:0.95rem;">Pregnancy Calculator & Growth Tracker</strong>
        <p style="opacity:0.6;font-size:0.83rem;margin:0.4rem 0 0;line-height:1.4;">Calculate your estimated due date, current gestational age, and track fetal growth milestones based on your last menstru...</p>
